overview: Award winning director, Mason, returns with Pornstar Workout 2, featuring an epic all star cast: Kagney Linn Karter, Shyla Stylez, Angelina Armani, Sadie West, Kelly Divine, Isis Taylor, Gracie Glam, and Madison Parker.  The movie features five visually stunning and extended workout scenarios and is shot in 16:9, 1080p HD.
title: Pornstar Workout 2
